	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />All this talk seems a little extreme, I do 16-bit sumchecks of my PRG and CHR dumps like it's 1985. If you don't have to worry about questionable game integrity, like pirates or porn ROMs, this method works reasonably well and is dead simple to implement on anything. There's a high probability for a repeat sum but I don't have one yet.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


