	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Yeah I agree that it seems overkill, I really think CRC32 would be just fine for this project. But since multiple people want it, I've put it in. All ROMs in the DB now have SHA1 hashes generated. For the time being, if you want to view it, hold the pointer over the CRC32 value of the ROM and the SHA1 will display in a tooltip.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
